data.description: Introducing 8997 Southern Charm Circle, a meticulously remodeled haven in the heart of Brooksville, Florida, offering not only modern luxury but also exclusive perks. This 2021-built home comes with a 12-month home warranty, providing new homeowners with peace of mind from the start. Additionally, we are generously covering 12 months of HOA dues, further enhancing the value of this exceptional property.    Step through the front door into an ambiance of sophistication and comfort. The thoughtful floor plan maximizes space and functionality, featuring tasteful upgrades like gleaming vinyl plank floors and designer finishes. The gourmet kitchen, complete with state-of-the-art appliances and granite countertops, is a dream for culinary enthusiasts.    One of the property's highlights is its prime location within the vibrant community of Spring Ridge. Residents enjoy exclusive access to the community pool—a perfect retreat for relaxation and socializing under the warm Florida sun. The nearby playground adds an extra layer of convenience for families, creating a space for little ones to play and make lasting memories.    Beyond the elegant abode, Brooksville beckons with a wealth of attractions and amenities. Nature enthusiasts will appreciate the proximity to parks and outdoor recreational areas, while history buffs can explore the rich historical sites that dot the landscape. The charming downtown area offers a blend of boutique shops, cozy cafes, and local eateries, creating a welcoming atmosphere for residents.    For those seeking adventure, Brooksville provides easy access to a myriad of outdoor activities, including hiking, biking, and water sports. The community's central location makes it a convenient hub for exploring nearby beaches, state parks, and cultural events.    8997 Southern Charm Circle is more than just a house; it's a lifestyle. Immerse yourself in the beauty of a home that seamlessly combines modern luxury with community amenities and the allure of Brooksville's diverse offerings. Don't miss the opportunity to make this residence your own and experience the best that Florida living has to offer.
